<title>trktk wtht</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 trktk wtht rby fy ạlqfạr ḍllt lys ly ʿzạʾ ạ̉w rjạʾ
 trkt ʿrsẖk ltḥyạ ʿbdk bmwtk ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb llfdạʾ
 ạlqrạr- ạʿdtny lḥḍnk ḍmmtny lṣdrk kswtny bbrk ạ̉qmtny fy bytk
 mbrrạ ṭwl ạlmdy̱
 mn ạlrdy̱ bmwtk ạ̉qmtny mn dẖl ạ̉tẖmy bạldm ḥrrtny
 wmʿ ạ̉sẖrạfk lqd ạ̉jlstny ạ̹dẖ qdtny ạly̱ ḥmạk bfdạk
 sạ̉ḥml ạlṣlyb ky ạ̉ḥyạ lk bạ dẖạtk stḥyạ by bḥbk
 ysẖdny kẖlạṣk ldrbk yʿydny ạly̱ ạlḥyạẗ bạlrjạʾ</lyrics>
